1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 2=

11
00:00:57,439 --> 00:00:59,159
If you like it this way

12
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,840
so be it.

13
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,319
Interesting.

14
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:18,200
Every time you complete a mission

15
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,040
you will receive a reward.

16
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:22,120
In six months

17
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:24,799
you'll get rid of the Lockjaw Drop.

18
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,319
Understood.

19
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:28,920
(My mother was a princess of Xichu.)

20
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,959
(Ten years ago,)

21
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,680
(she died in a palace fire.)

22
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,599
(Your face is exactly like hers.)

23
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,959
(In the Palace)
(It takes three days to temper jade.)

24
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,840
(Let me see how much trouble)

25
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:44,159
(this face of yours
can stir in the palace.)

26
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,680
(She... she has no feet.)

27
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:51,280
(She's floating!)

28
00:01:54,159 --> 00:01:55,000
(Consort Chu!)

29
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:59,799
(Consort Chu,
who died in a fire, has returned!)

30
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,919
Mother

31
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:15,800
what expression
do you think they'll have

32
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,520
when they see you again?

33
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:27,840
From today on

34
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,919
your name is Mei Lin.

35
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,560
And you're the princess of Xichu.

36
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,240
I understand.

37
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,719
I need you to get close to

38
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:40,080
Prince Xuanlie
at the Drilling Ground tomorrow.

39
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,439
Infiltrate his side

40
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,840
and be my inside source.

41
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,560
(Murong Xuanlie, The Eldest Prince)
(He's ruthless and cruel.)

42
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,639
(Crippled me and cost me the battle.)

43
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,719
(No matter what he does,)

44
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,319
(do not act on your own.)

45
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:56,080
(Wait for my signal.)

46
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,759
(Of course.)

47
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,879
Hurry, keep up.

48
00:02:58,919 --> 00:02:59,680
Father.

49
00:02:59,680 --> 00:02:59,960
Kneel.

50
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,199
I won a great victory this time

51
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,120
and brought back many Xichu remnants.

52
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,080
Why not let them fight like beasts

53
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,719
(Murong Che, Emperor of Daliang)
to entertain you?

54
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,280
(Pei Du, The Emperor's Confidant)
How come killing a few bound men

55
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,000
awaiting death shows Daliang's might?

56
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:14,039
Your way of awing the world,
Your Highness,

57
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,719
is truly eye-opening.

58
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,639
(The imperial elite see us
as mere ants,)

59
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,039
(crushing us.)

60
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:30,199
(But I will carve out
my own path to survive!)

61
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,960
Mr. Pei, you're a civil official.

62
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,919
You don't get it.

63
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:37,879
Training without bloodshed
isn't training at all.

64
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,199
Xuanlie.

65
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:44,560
What?

66
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,800
Jinghe, you can't even stand
the blood of Xichu remnants?

67
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:50,439
Do you still miss your motherland?

68
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,080
Watch your words, Xuanlie.

69
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,439
If that's the case

70
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:57,400
then prove to Father.

71
00:03:57,919 --> 00:04:01,240
Show him your loyalty to Daliang.

72
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,439
Kill them.

73
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:06,719
(Clever trap.)

74
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,960
(If Murong Jinghe kills us,)

75
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,360
(the world will call him cruel.)

76
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:12,400
(If he doesn't,)

77
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,879
(they'll doubt his loyalty to Daliang.)

78
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,360
(He's still useful to me.)

79
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,360
(He must not fall from power again.)

80
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,680
Kill me instead.

81
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:36,519
I'm Mei Lin, princess of Xichu.

82
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,120
I beg Your Majesty for mercy.

83
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:40,720
Take my life, and spare these people.

84
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,000
Bring her forward.

85
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,160
Move!

86
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,360
They're alike.

87
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:50,160
(Consort Li)

88
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,319
(Consort Li)
They really are.

89
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,120
(Yiyi!)

90
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:00,199
(Yiyi,)

91
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,120
(have you come back?)

92
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:05,040
But she's not truly her.

93
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,319
Then let it be as you wish.

94
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:10,560
Your life for these slaves' lives.

95
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,639
(For revenge,)

96
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:14,000
(anyone can become my blade,)

97
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,399
(even myself.)

98
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,360
As a princess, I

99
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,839
was sustained by my people.

100
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,399
Giving my own life

101
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,680
to save the commoners

102
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,399
is worth it.

103
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:49,980
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

104
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:53,200
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

105
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:56,540
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

106
